SaolaPy
==================================
[![License: Celonis Tools License Agreement](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-Celonis%20Tools%20License%20Agreement-brightgreen)](https://celonis.github.io/pycelonis/license.html)

Repository for SaolaPy, a Pandas DataFrame interface to SaolaDB.

## Development Setup

### Environment

**SaolaPy** supports `python >=3.8`.

### Development Dependencies & Pre-Commit Hooks
Create new virtual environment and install required development dependencies (extra index is required to install pycelonis):
```bash
pip install --extra-index-url=https://pypi.celonis.cloud/ -e ".[dev]" && pre-commit install
```

Check if pre-commit hooks are installed correctly.
```bash
pre-commit run --all-files
```

## Testing
In order to run the tests simply execute:
```bash
pytest ./tests --vcr-record=none -n auto
```
